{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Slimg chased by space pirates, is forced to land on a mysterious planet. In order to leave this planet, Slimg began his adventure on this planet</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/new1.gif?t=1738403196\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The SR400 planet has a total of four regions with completely different styles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sdog village: The creatures in sdog village love pumpkins, and there is a mysterious ability in the village that allows other creatures to freely grow and shrink.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/new5.gif?t=1738403196\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Rainforest: In the depths of the rainforest, there are several temples where a mysterious female warrior landed in a spaceship. Could this be the key to leaving this planet?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/new3.gif?t=1738403196\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Volcano: The volcano, which had been dormant for a long time, began to erupt again, and the constantly falling boulders caused unbearable suffering to the creatures living there.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/new2.gif?t=1738403196\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Icefield: The rulers of the Icefield seem to control the entire planet, and all disasters seem to arise from it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/new4.gif?t=1738403196\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Eecrypt</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each area has decryption elements that match its style, solving puzzles and obtaining items that make characters stronger.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Please help Slei Dog leave this planet and explore various regions to its fullest!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738403196","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738403196","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/b5f857bc9b8e8d65a185358037e4114d63f21ef6/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738403196","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/b5f857bc9b8e8d65a185358037e4114d63f21ef6/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738403196","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Slimg chased by space pirates, is forced to land on a mysterious planet. In order to leave this planet, Slimg began his adventure on this planet</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/new1.gif?t=1738403196\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Explore</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The SR400 planet has a total of four regions with completely different styles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sdog village: The creatures in sdog village love pumpkins, and there is a mysterious ability in the village that allows other creatures to freely grow and shrink.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3331120/extras/new5.gif?t=1738403196\" /></p><p class=\"bb_pa